      "description": "We are proud to present this collector-grade masterpiece, preserved in flawless, showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a pristine exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and mechanically superb, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. Experience the confidence of owning a vehicle that has been curated for the most demanding standards.",
      "price": 48900.0,
